room_title: Escape room "Th3 C0d3" by Escapology St. Peters in St. Louis
room_address: 4105 N. Cloverleaf Dr. Suite B St. Peters, MO 63376
room_description:
Cambridge, Massachusetts, January 23, 2015
Your Cyber Crime unit has to face the most challenging task yet. An anonymous tip places Nitr0, the world's most famous hacker, at an apartment in Cambridge. Upon arriving, you receive a video message from Nitr0 himself, saying that he set this trap for you. You will be framed for the biggest virtual heist in history. Unless you find a way to stop Nitr0...
